Weapon_Proficiency_Smg_Barter_Rookie des: Do you really think any homeless bum can walk into my shop and get a gun? If you want to get something, you first need to prove you are worth my time wasted... And don't look at those shinies in the corner - they are for Elite only! Here is what you need to do first: Bring me several SMGs toys. That should do for now. Shoo!
